me: 'home',\r\n  component: Home,\r\n  beforeEnter(to, from, next) {\r\n    // TODO\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 第三种：组件内的钩子。\r\n``` js\r\nbeforeRouteEnter(to, from, next) {\r\n  // do someting\r\n  // 在渲染该组件的对应路由被 confirm 前调用\r\n},\r\nbeforeRouteUpdate(to, from, next) {\r\n  // do someting\r\n  // 在当前路由改变，但是依然渲染该组件是调用\r\n},\r\nbeforeRouteLeave(to, from ,next) {\r\n  // do someting\r\n  // 导航离开该组件的对应路由时被调用\r\n}\r\n```","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/206/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/206/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"menus":[]},"__N_SSG":true}